
If your using Firefox as browser and you want to run this app
under https you should add the app's certificates to firefox
accepted CA

- open the top-right menu
- settings -> privacy&security
- go down until you see "certificates"
- click on "view certificates"
- in the bar on top of the new window go to "authorities"
- click on "import"
- select your certificate (.crt)
- tick the first choice "... identify websites" (tick both if you wanna be sure)
- click "ok"
- refresh your page and now your good to go :)

